text: Castelnuovo della Misericordia is a village in Tuscany, central Italy, administratively a frazione of the comune of Rosignano Marittimo, province of Livorno. At the time of the 2011 census its population was 843. The village is about 24 km from Livorno and 5 km from Rosignano Marittimo. ==Bibliography== * == External links == * Category:Frazioni of the Province of Livorno
